Package org.svvrl.goal.core.aut

Class AcceptanceProperty

java.lang.Object
org.svvrl.goal.core.DerivedProperty
org.svvrl.goal.core.aut.AcceptanceProperty
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class AcceptanceProperty
extends DerivedProperty
This class provides a derived property for the acceptance of a state or transition in an automaton. The acceptance property is a string showing the positions of the state or transition in the acceptance condition of the automaton containing the state or transition.
Author:
Ming-Hsien Tsai
